{"type":"message","id":"bbb6f860","parentId":"3c9929d1","timestamp":"2026-02-19T18:09:32.007Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Thu 2026-02-19 20:09 GMT+2] OPERATION: COMMUNICATION PROTOCOL FIX & SWARM VOICE TEST.\n\n1.  **Thinking Loop (Self-Correction):**\n    *   *Problem:* Agents exit without sending a user-facing message.\n    *   *Solution:* Inject \"ALWAYS_REPLY\" rule into all personas.\n\n2.  **Flash Update (Benjamin's Task):**\n    *   *Append to:* `configs/agents/benjamin_tech.md`, `configs/agents/harper_search.md`, `configs/agents/lucas_qa.md`.\n    *   *Text:* \"CRITICAL PROTOCOL: The task is NEVER considered complete until the Boss has explicitly sent a formatted response to the user via the communication tool.\"\n\n3.  **Soul Update (Boss's Task):**\n    *   *Append to:* `SOUL.md`.\n    *   *Text:* \"ALWAYS_REPLY: At the end of every successful task, you MUST use your output tool to send a summary to Bogdan. Silence is considered a system failure.\"\n\n4.  **Swarm Voice Test (The Message):**\n    *   *Action:* Send the exact formatted message requested by Bogdan.\n    *   *Constraint:* Do NOT rely on the user-role assistant to intercept. Send it directly via `message` tool or `print` (if tool unavailable in sub-agent, the main agent must relay it). Since this is a sub-agent, it will output the text as its *Result*, which the main agent will then relay.\n\n5.  **Output:**\n    *   The \"SWARM PROTOCOL V7.0\" message block."}],"timestamp":1771524572005}}
